title: 2014-10-23.The Anthony Cumia Show
description: Episode 047: Ant gives everyone a pool update as well as one on how Big A is feeling after yesterday's show with Jade, we hear about sexting, and Ant schools Rat on sex now versus then. Ant waxes about his old CB radio, goes through a few Tinder pics, talks about hookers, we see a note from Bobo's doctor, and Ant lifts the show ban on Bobo even though KtC doesn't agree. We then go through a list of teachers who've had sex with students, Ant takes a couple of calls, and we hear police audio from Bristol Palin. Against his better judgment, @BrokenCurse gets unblocked by Anthony thanks to Ticket University, we watch a video of a tittie twerker, one from religious extremists, and find out that the official TACS Paltalk chatroom is up. Ant shows us a video from drunken prankster Australians, tells us about some pranks they used to play on Joe Currie, we watch a clip of a crying criminal, wish Keith Robinson a happy birthday, see some foreign chicks dancing, and he finishes up with an educational YouTube video
